emand%20for%20domain-specific%2C%20customized%20machine%20learning%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOther%20investors%20include%20General%20Catalyst%2C%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20Liquid%202%20Ventures%2C%20and%20Paul%20Graham.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECTGT%2C%20a%20startup%20focused%20on%20helping%20enterprise%20clients%20train%20and%20deploy%20machine%20learning%20models%20at%20lower%20cost%2C%20has%20raised%20%247.2%20million%20in%20a%20funding%20round%20led%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-venture-capital-firms-investing-artificial-intelligence-machine-learning-2023-2%23gradient-ventures-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGradient%20Ventures%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google's%20AI-geared%20venture%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20shows%20investors%20are%20still%20optimistic%20about%20startups%20developing%20tools%20to%20train%20models%2C%20as%20companies%20like%20Google%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-3-openai-chatgpt-elon-musk-xai-sam-altman-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20jostle%20to%20produce%20a%20foundation%20model%20more%20capable%20than%20all%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECyril%20Gorlla%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20CTGT%2C%20says%20many%20businesses%20have%20access%20to%20these%20generalized%20models%20but%20can't%20deploy%20them%20because%20of%20the%20inherent%20risks.%20It%20may%20hallucinate%20a%20response%20or%20display%20bias.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20healthcare%20provider%20can't%20risk%20a%20medical%20chatbot%20giving%20dangerous%20advice.%20A%20tech%20company%20wouldn't%20want%20a%20digital%20agent%20referring%20customers%20to%20its%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECTGT's%20solution%20allows%20enterprise%20clients%20to%20take%20one%20of%20these%20off-the-shelf%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-models-microsoft-openai-meta-google-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efoundation%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20imbue%20it%20with%20their%20brand%20voice%20and%20data.%20It%20claims%20to%20lower%20the%20massive%20amounts%20of%20computing%20resources%20needed%20through%20a%20process%20called%20feature%20learning%2C%20where%20a%20system%20learns%20to%20recognize%20patterns%20and%20structures%20in%20raw%20data%20without%20being%20explicitly%20programmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGorlla%20says%20the%20platform%20actively%20monitors%20and%20audits%20a%20client's%20custom%20models%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20better%20spot%20and%20eliminate%20unwanted%20behavior.%20Enterprises%20can%20also%20refine%20and%20retrain%20models%20on%20the%20fly%20without%20the%20need%20to%20take%20models%20offline%20for%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVig%20Sachidananda%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Gradient%2C%20says%20the%20startup%20addresses%20a%20need%20for%20more%20reliable%20and%20bespoke%20alternatives%20to%20generalized%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20AI%20models%20rapidly%20progress%20in%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20Sachidananda%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20models%20take%20on%20more%20tasks%20and%20those%20with%20increasing%20complexity%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20need%20from%20enterprises%20for%20systems%20that%20can%20help%20improve%20safety%2C%20provide%20more%20accurate%20responses%2C%20and%20mitigate%20biases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20excited%20about%20CTGT%20as%20they're%20developing%20a%20novel%20approach%20to%20tackle%20these%20problems%20by%20helping%20enterprises%20interpret%20and%20control%20how%20models%20internally%20understand%20concepts%2C%20such%20as%20those%20that%20can%20relate%20to%20unsafe%20or%20unexpected%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20investors%20in%20the%20company's%20seed%20funding%20round%20include%20General%20Catalyst%2C%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20Liquid%202%20Ventures%2C%20and%20angel%20investors%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaul-graham-told-elon-musk-approach-doge-wo