%2C%20an%20upmarket%20area%20in%20Mysuru%2C%20as%20compensation%20for%20the%20use%20of%203.16%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Kesare%20village%20near%20the%20city.%20An%20anti-corruption%20activist%20had%20complained%20that%20this%20had%20caused%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%2045%20crore%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20has%20maintained%20that%20there%20was%20no%20wrongdoing%20in%20the%20transactions%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20plots%20were%20gifted%20to%20his%20wife%20by%20her%20brother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriting%20to%20one%20of%20the%20complainants%2C%20the%20Lokayukta%20had%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20there%20was%20not%20enough%20evidence%20to%20conduct%20an%20investigation%20against%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20the%20charges%20seemed%20civil%20in%20nature%20and%20not%20%26quot%3Bsuitable%20for%20criminal%20charges%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20said%20it%20has%20faith%20in%20the%20Lokayukta%20but%20insisted%20that%20the%20investigation%20was%20not%20conducted%20properly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20full%20confidence%20in%20the%20Lokayukta%2C%20whereas%20the%20police%20officers%20who%20have%20investigated%20have%20been%20transferred%2C%20appointed%2C%20given%20postings%20by%20the%20same%20Siddaramaiah.%20We%20cannot%20expect%20a%20fair%20inquiry%20and%20this%20is%20an%20eyewash.%20If%20Siddaramaiah%20wants%20to%20come%20clean%2C%20he%20should%20hand%20over%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20otherwise%20a%20high%20court-monitored%20investigation%20should%20be%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20being%20okay%20with%20Lokayukta%20orders%20or%20rulings%20as%20long%20as%20they%20were%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20said%20in%20the%20beginning%20itself%2C%20when%20BJP%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20did%20their%20padayatra%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Mysuru%2C%20that%20it%20(allegation)%20is%20politically%20motivated.%20His%20(Siddaramaiah)%20signature%20was%20not%20there%2C%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it.%20His%20family%20had%20lost%20the%20property%20and%20had%20asked%20for%20a%20claim%2C%20everyone%20does%20that%20whether%20it%20is%20me%20or%20you%2C%20and%20he%20was%20given%20(alternative%20sites).%20There%20was%20no%20demand%20for%20allotment%20in%20a%20specific%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivakumar%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20should%20be%20evidence%20to%20file%20any%20case%2C%20but%20in%20this%20case%20there%20was%20no%20evidence.%20Lokayukta%20have%20done%20their%20duty%2C%20if%20they%20(complainants)%20have%20any%20objections%2C%20let%20them%20fight%20(legally)...%20Lokayukta%20is%20not%20just%20the%20police%2C%20it%20is%20an%20independent%20body%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20no%20control%20over%20it.%20If%20any%20official%20has%20to%20be%20appointed%20to%20the%20body%2C%20it%20is%20only%20after%20taking%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Lokayukta%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740053880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fsbe5psm_siddaramaiah_625x300_18_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmuda-case-siddaramaiah-congress-karnataka-bjp-questions-lokayukta-clean-chit-to-siddaramaiah-congress-hits-back-7754811%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Lokayukta's%20clean%20chit%20to%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20in%20the%20alleged%20MUDA%20land%20scam%20has%20triggered%20a%20political%20slugfest%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20alleging%20that%20the%20state%20handpicked%20the%20officers%20investigating%20the%20case%20and%20the%20Congress%20hitting%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmuda-