itude%20for%20the%20driver's%20selfless%20and%20heroic%20actions.%20One%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20whole%20movie%20dude!%20God%20bless%20the%20driver%20and%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BGreat%20driver!%20Also%2C%20a%20Rapido%20person%20once%20told%20me%20that%20there%20are%20no%20waiting%20charges%20in%20Rapido%20like%20other%20apps%20have.%20So%20I%20guess%20there%20wasn't%20a%20way%20to%20charge%20extra%20either.%20Congratulations%20to%20the%20father%20though!%20Cheers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BShare%20on%20LinkedIn.%20Rapido%20loves%20to%20recognise%20their%20drivers%20and%20even%20reward%20them%20in%20few%20cases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740052200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fcr3k1ta8_driver_625x300_20_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Frapido-driver-helps-woman-deliver-baby-in-his-cab-internet-calls-him-a-hero-7754530%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incredible%20story%20was%20shared%20on%20Reddit%20by%20the%20man%20who%20had%20booked%20the%20ride%20for%20his%20cook%20and%20her%20pregnant%20wife%20and%20has%20since%20warmed%20the%20hearts%20of%20many%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Frapido-driver-helps-woman-deliver-baby-in-his-cab-internet-calls-him-a-hero-7754530%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rekha%20Gupta%20Takes%20Over%20As%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister.%20What%20Her%20Day%201%20Looks%20Like%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20first-time%20MLA%20Rekha%20Gupta%20had%20a%20packed%20schedule%20on%20Day%201%20of%20her%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20taking%20oath%20along%20with%20her%20council%20of%20ministers%20of%20six%20leaders%20this%20afternoon%2C%20she%20went%20to%20her%20office%20at