0contested%20and%20GPS-denied%20environments%2C%20growing%20problems%20in%20modern%20conflicts%20like%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20It%20began%20focusing%20on%20designing%20solutions%20for%20drone%20communication%20challenges%20in%202022%2C%20and%20it%20started%20mass%20production%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESine%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-jamming-resistant-drones-may-expose-western-vulnerability-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-GPS%20navigation%20systems%20to%20avoid%20jamming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20relying%20on%20time-of-flight%20calculations%20to%20determine%20location.%20Its%20products%20are%20being%20employed%20by%20over%2050%20drone%20makers%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20outside%20of%20the%20country%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20Andriy%20Chulyk%20told%20BI%20that%20knowing%20the%20battlefield%20is%20critical%20to%20designing%20technology%20for%20a%20war%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20defeat%20the%20electronic%20warfare%20capabilities%20of%20a%20major%20military%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20try%20and%20test%20different%20kind%20of%20things%26quot%3B%20and%20be%20connected%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%20%26quot%3Bto%20receive%20constant%20feedback%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20drone%20carrying%20a%20fake%20bomb%20flies%20against%20a%20bright%20blue%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b621aa7bb3f854015d43a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20electronic%20warfare%20has%20forced%20Ukrainian%20drone%20operators%20to%20adapt%20%E2%80%94%20and%20employ%20EW%20tactics%20of%20their%20own.%3Cp%3ESine.Engineering%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESine's%20data%20chips%20are%20as%20small%20as%20an%20SD%20card%20and%20designed%20to%20facilitate%20drone%20navigation%20to%20targets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-jammers-killing-it-new-kursk-push-russian-bloggers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20satellites%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20off-the-shelf%20drone%20systems%20and%20GPS-guided%20munitions%20rely%20on%20satellite%20information%2C%20but%20drones%20equipped%20with%20Sine%20technology%20depend%20on%20signals%20from%20a%20communication%20module%20that%20keeps%20track%20of%20the%20drone's%20location%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20somewhat%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20pre-GPS%20%26quot%3Bdead%20reckoning%26quot%3B%20by%20pilots.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESine's%20hardware%20and%20software%20tools%20are%20intended%20to%20provide%20reliable%20navigation%20and%20flight%20control%2C%20as%20well%20as%20resistance%20to%20GPS%20jamming.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20working%20on%20how%20to%20keep%20drones%20flying%20on%20radio%20signals%20even%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-showing-us-troops-fight-hide-in-electromagnetic-spectrum-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtested%20environments%20filled%20with%20frequency%20jamming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20electronic%20warfare%20that%20involves%20flooding%20frequencies%20with%20noise%20to%20disrupt%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChulyk%20and%20Sine's%20Chief%20Strategy%20Officer%20Andriy%20Zvirko%20said%20that%20their%20drone%20parts%20are%20self-produced%20and%20affordable%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20crucial%20to%20scaling%20up%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20comms%20technologies%20for%20drones%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20not%20only%20about%20price%3B%20it's%20about%20how%20they%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Zvirko%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20good%20provider.%20That's%20why%20we%20created%20our%20own%20because%20we%20have%20seen%20this%20gap%20on%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20Sine's%20products%20are%20active%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20but%20one%20of%20its%20newer%20focuses%20being%20tested%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20army%20is%20drone%20swarming%2C%20which%20involves%20using%20autonomy%20to%20pilot%20multiple%20drones%20to%20targets.%20Drone%20swarming%20isn't%20a%20new%20concept%2C%20but%20Chulyk%20and%20Zvirko%20said%20that%20many%20drone%20developers%20have%20different%20ideas%20of%20what%20the%20capabilities%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20vision%20involves%20an%20operator%20being%20able%20to%20run%20multiple%20uncrewed%20vehicles%20at%20once%20and%20switch%20to%20the%20drone%20they%20want%20to%20at%20a%20given%20moment.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%2C%26quot%3B%20Chulyk%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20will%20make%20our%20military%20forces%20more%20effective%20because%20it%20will%20be%20possible%20to%20operate%20a%20lot%20of%20drones%20in%20the%20same%20time%20from%20one%20or%20two%20operators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holds%20a%20small%20data%20card%20against%20a%20grey%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b621ddeb4be2fff9a505c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESine%20is%20working%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20technical%20solutions%20to%20challenges%20presented%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3Cp%3ESine.Engineering%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESine%20is%20working%20to%20achieve%20autonomy%20in%20drone%20technology%2C%20but%20a%20key%20challenge%20is%20the%20amount%20of%20data%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20calculate%20for%20navigation%20and%20precision.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20hasn't%20seen%20widespread%20usage%20on%20the%20battlefield%20yet%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tayfun.in.ua%2Fen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkraine's%20special%20drone%20unit%20Typhoon%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20BI%20this%20month%2C%20but%20such%20a%20capability%20could%2