.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tech-jobs-basic-coding-programming-skills-education-needed-recruiters-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%2025%20years%20after%20first%20being%20exposed%20to%20AI%20research%20in%20my%20undergrad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20career%20in%20academia%2C%20focusing%20on%20technology%20capable%20of%20human%20reasoning.%20Around%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20became%20interested%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gains-self-driving-cars-automotive-ai-technology-toyota-aurora-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eself-driving%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20Uber%20in%202017%20and%20became%20the%20chief%20scientist%20of%20its%20self-driving%20unit.%20I%20wanted%20to%20push%20self-driving%20technology%20in%20the%20real%20world.%20However%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20the%20industry%20was%20using%20a%20capital-intensive%20approach%20that%20I%20didn't%20think%20could%20scale%20self-driving%20vehicles.%20I%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20build%20my%20own%20company%20with%20an%20AI-first%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20I%20founded%20Waabi.%20We're%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-most-promising-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20focused%20on%20developing%20self-driving%20trucks.%20We've%20raised%20over%20%24280%20million%2C%20receiving%20investment%20from%20best-in-class%20investors%20like%20Nvidia%20and%20Uber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaabi%20raised%20large%20amounts%20during%20our%20two%20rounds%20of%20funding%20so%20far%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20building%20the%20company%20for%20an%20exit.%20I%20want%20to%20transform%20the%20world.%20Having%20the%20best%20people%20in%20the%20industry%20supporting%20us%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20help%20in%20the%20endeavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b30829f4-65b9-4afc-b40c-bf2683e66499%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20Waabi%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20unleashing%20the%20power%20of%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20nearly%20four%20years%20at%20Uber.%20It%20was%20a%20great%20stepping%20stone%20for%20entrepreneurship.%20I%20learned%20so%20much%20about%20building%20a%20business%20and%20being%20an%20executive.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ceo-fleets-robotaxis-will-take-a-while-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDara%20Khosrowshahi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Uber's%20CEO%2C%20became%20a%20mentor%20to%20me%2C%20which%20has%20been%20an%20asset%20in%20my%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHad%20I%20started%20Waabi%20as%20an%20academic%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20would%20be%20as%20successful%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20Waabi%20because%20I%20didn't%20think%20the%20industry's%20capital-intensive%20approach%2C%20which%20has%20historically%20involved%20fleets%20of%20vehicles%20driving%20physical%20distances%20for%20tests%2C%20would%20generate%20scalable%20technology%20that%20could%20be%20deployed%20in%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20a%20system%20with%20bits%20and%20pieces%20of%20AI%20playing%20a%20small%20role%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20single%20AI%20system%20that%20can%20safely%20perform%20all%20the%20necessary%20tests%20for%20self-driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20building%20an%20Al-generated%20simulation%20system%20for%20testing%20and%20training%20vehicles%20that%20was%20the%20same%20as%20the%20real%20world.%20My%20background%20in%20AI%20helped%20me%20foresee%20this%20technology%20years%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaabi%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Toronto%2C%20where%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20AI%20talent.%20We%20have%20trucks%20in%20Texas%20that%20are%20driving%20autonomously%20on%20public%20roads%20for%20commercial%20operations%2C%20both%20through%20a%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwaabi.ai%2Fwaabi-uber-freight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUber%20Freight%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20also%20direct-to-customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254dbe275-2238-403f-af6e-dd0a0b4a8b34%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe've%20raised%20more%20than%20%24280%20million%20and%20are%20backed%20by%20investors%20like%20Uber%20and%20Nvidia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20done%20two%20rounds%20of%20financing.%20Our%20Series%20A%20was%20led%20by%20Khosla%20Ventures.%20It%20was%20too%20large%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bseed%26quot%3B%20round%2C%20but%20it%20was%20done%20in%20the%20company's%20first%20week.%20We%20raised%20%2483.5%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20Series%20A%20investors%20are%20all%20excited%20about%20Waabi.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-vinod-khosla-fixing-ai-image-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVinod%20Khosla%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20founded%20Khosla%20Ventures%2C%20is%20himself%20very%20bullish%20about%20our%20potential.%20This%20support%20is%20so%20valuable%20because%20as%20a%20company%20continues%20its%20journey%2C%20your%20current%20investors%20and%20your%20reputation%20help%20to%20tell%20your%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20brief%20three-and-a-half-year%20history%2C%20we've%20hit%20ambitious%20milestone%20goals.%20When%20I%20pitched%20during%20our%20Series%20A%2C%20I%20mentioned%20our%20plans%20for%20the%20simulator%20and%20trucks%2C%20and%20we%20managed%20to%20hit%20our%20milestones%20exactly%20as%20I%20pitched.%20This%20resonated%20well%20with%20investors%20for%20our%20second%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20some%20challenges.%20There%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fsanfrancisco%2Fnews%2Fnhtsa-robotaxi-cruise-pay-penalty-failing-report-san-francisco-crash-involving-pedestrian%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCruise%2520suspended%2520operations%2520just%2520over%2Cby%2520a%2520human%252Ddriven%2520vehicle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccident%20with%20an%20autonomous%20vehicle%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%20The%20market%20was%20quite%20tough%20after%20that%2C%20and%20investors%20were%20concerned%20about%20how%20one%20incident%20could%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20value%20of%20the%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20concerns%20about%20whether%20the%20population%20wanted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-self-driving-cars-work-and-their-safety-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eself-driving%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Investors%20will%20always%20ask%20you%20about%20risks%2C%20so%20we%20explained%20them.%20Our%20safety%20approach%2C%20which%20is%20simulation-first%20and%20avoids%20adding%20risk%20to%20the%20roads%20before%20the%20technology%20is%20ready%2C%20resonated%20with%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dee69511-4a67-4540-93b9-cbfe16a4d554%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20cap%20table%20explained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20announced%20our%20second%20round%20of%20financing%20last%20June%20and%20raised%20%24200%20million.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20oversubscribed%20round%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20say%20no%20to%20people.%20We%20ended%20up%20raising%20more%20than%20we%20intended%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20very%20strategic%20about%20the%20types%20of%20investors%20we%20wanted%20to%20bring%20to%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpulley-cap-table-management-startup-raises-40m-from-founders-fund-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecap%20table%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20that%20we'd%20have%20the%20best%20in%20class%20to%20help%20us%20in%20the%20company's%20next%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20side%2C%20there%20was%20the%20AI%20bucket.%20We%20had%20investment%20from%20Khosla%20Ventures%20%E2%80%94%20who%20really%20understood%20generative%20AI%20before%20anybody%20else%20and%20have%20also%20invested%20in%20OpenAI%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20logistics%2C%20we%20wanted%20a%20forward-looking%20shipper%2C%20which%20was%20Ingka%20Investments%2C%20the%20investment%20arm%20of%20Ingka%20Group%2C%20who%20operate%20IKEA.%20We%20also%20had%20participation%20from%20Uber%2C%20who%20jointly%20led%20the%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20we%20wanted%20original%20equipment%20manufacturers%20(OEMs)%2C%20which%20is%20very%20important%20when%20you%20build%20technology%20for%20self-driving.%20We%20had%20Volvo%20Group%20Venture%20Capital%2C%20Scania%20Invest%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Porsche%20Automobil%20Holding%20SE%2C%20invest%20in%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20differentiated%20technology%20is%20one%20reason%20behind%20our%20success.%20Investors%20were%20coming%20around%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-transforming-technical-work-vercel-julius-developers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20physical%20world%20and%20saw%20Waabi%20as%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a105e932-d66e-4fa9-b8ee-7d3242372aea%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaving%20tremendous%20supporters%20has%20been%20very%20helpful%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20one%20of%20our%20investors%2C%20but%20we%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwaabi.ai%2Fnvidia-drivethor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epartner%20with%20them%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20the%20generative%20AI%20compute%20that%20drives%20our%20trucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20personal%20relationship%20with%20Nvidia%20goes%20back%20a%20decade.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-advice-students-10-year-future-prediction-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20always%20been%20a%20big%20supporter%20of%20my%20research.%20When%20I%20was%20an%20academic%2C%20he'd%20come%20to%20academic%20events.%20He's%20very%20personable%20and%20someone%20I%20look%20up%20to%20in%20terms%20of%20bu