A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fspring-gardening-tools-accessories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egardening%20and%20landscaping%3C%2Fa%3E%20grew%20gradually.%20I%20thought%20about%20trying%20to%20grow%20food%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%20but%20felt%20overwhelmed%20with%20everything%20I%20needed%20to%20learn%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20my%20poor%20track%20record%20with%20houseplants%20which%20added%20to%20my%20feelings%20of%20inadequacy.%20But%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshoppers-ditch-supermarkets-to-grow-their-own-fruit-and-vegetables-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprice%20of%20produce%3C%2Fa%3E%20ever-increasing%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20I%20figured%20even%20if%20I%20could%20grow%20a%20few%20vegetables%2C%20it%20could%20help%20offset%20my%20family's%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243cd9c1f-644d-468c-be1e-f8df2eaca339%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20do%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20helped%20me%20put%20my%20early%20worries%20about%20gardening%20to%20bed.%20%26quot%3BJust%20throw%20it%20in%20the%20ground%20and%20see%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20She%20helped%20me%20realize%20that%20starting%20a%20garden%20was%20not%20about%20growing%20plants%20perfectly%2C%20but%20learning%20through%20trial%20and%20error.%20I%20embraced%20her%20outlook%20and%20built%20my%20first%20raised%20garden%20bed%20from%20wood%20planks%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20screws%20in%20the%20spring%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20me%20get%20started%2C%20I%20took%20an%20hour-long%20spring%20gardening%20class%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wyldecenter.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWylde%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20non-profit%20nature%20and%20education%20center%20in%20Atlanta.%20The%20instructor%20taught%20us%20how%20to%20make%20miniature%20greenhouses%20for%20seeds%20by%20cutting%20a%20few%20holes%20into%20empty%20milk%20jugs%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20using%20a%20good%20soil%20that%20provides%20organic%20nutrients%20for%20seedlings%20to%20help%20them%20start%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20planted%20basil%2C%20tomatillo%2C%20and%20eggplant%20seeds%20in%20class.%20Using%20the%20same%20method%2C%20I%20started%20tomatoes%2C%20corn%2C%20and%20lettuce%20at%20home.%20I%20placed%20all%20of%20them%20on%20my%20front%20porch%20so%20they%20would%20get%20plenty%20of%20sun%20and%20rain.%20Once%20the%20seedlings%20outgrew%20the%20milk%20jugs%2C%20I%20transplanted%20the%20strongest%20ones%20into%20my%20garden%20bed.%20It%20was%20exhilarating%20to%20watch%20everything%20grow%20with%20nature%20doing%20most%20of%20the%20work.%20%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20raised%20bed%20in%20a%20backyard%20garden%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b5e5cd7bb3f854015d384d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20started%20small%2C%20with%20one%20raised%20bed%20in%202022.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sheeka%20Sanahori%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afae02ff-6acd-45b0-a9da-688282c07762%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrial%20and%20error%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20mistakes%20the%20first%20year.%20I%20didn't%20know%20I%20needed%20to%20prune%20tomatoes%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20grow%20fruit%20rather%20than%20grow%20into%20bushy%20plants%20almost%20as%20tall%20as%20me.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20the%20tomatoes%20were%20scarce%20and%20small.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20growing%20season%2C%20I%20searched%20for%20answers%20online%20and%20watched%20a%20couple%20of%20videos%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20identify%20which%20stems%20to%20remove%20from%20the%20tomato%20plant.%20I%20also%20learned%20that%20I%20waited%20too%20long%20to%20harvest%20the%20lettuce%20and%20it%20bolted%20and%20tasted%20bitter.%20The%20eggplants%20and