rbon%20capture%20and%20storage%20market%20by%202050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Meta%20became%20the%20first%20big%20name%20in%20the%20industry%20to%20embrace%20the%20tech%20when%20the%20large%20southern%20utility%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.entergynewsroom.com%2Fnews%2Fentergy-louisiana-power-meta-s-data-center-in-richland-parish%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEntergy%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company%20had%20agreed%20to%20fund%20a%20large%20carbon%20capture%20and%20storage%20project%20in%20Louisiana.%20The%20deal%20will%20help%20Meta%20offset%20emissions%20from%20a%20%2410%20billion%20data%20center%20campus%20it%20is%20planning%20in%20the%20state%20that%20will%20be%20powered%20by%20three%20new%20natural%20gas-fired%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chevron.com%2Fnewsroom%2F2025%2Fq1%2Fpower-solutions-for-us-data-centers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChevron%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20build%20natural%20gas%20plants%20using%20carbon%20capture%2C%20citing%20the%20soaring%20demand%20from%20data%20center%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20piping%20carbon%20emissions%20underground%20is%20not%20new.%20Oil%20and%20gas%20extraction%20companies%20have%20pumped%20compressed%2C%20liquid%20carbon%20dioxide%20into%20wells%20for%20decades%20to%20help%20force%20out%20more%20fossil%20fuels.%20Using%20the%20technique%20at%20a%20scale%20large%20enough%20to%20begin%20significantly%20mitigating%20climate%20warming%20emissions%2C%20however%2C%20has%20been%20considered%20both%20enormously%20costly%20and%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20data%20center%20boom%2C%20generated%20by%20the%20race%20to%20develop%20and%20commercialize%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20has%20suddenly%20brightened%20the%20outlook.%20Leading%20data%20center%20builders%20include%20the%20deepest-pocketed%20companies%20in%20the%20world.%20Some%20of%20them%20appear%20willing%20to%20pay%20the%20kind%20of%20hefty%20premiums%20for%20emission-free%20electricity%20that%20would%20justify%20the%20costs%20of%20capture%20and%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20an%20'aha'%20moment%20that%20it's%20actually%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%20that%20are%20very%20interested%20in%20these%20power%20plants%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jerry%20Ashcroft%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Crescent%20Midstream%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fcrescent-midstream-selected-to-develop-an-integrated-carbon-capture-solution-for-entergy-natural-gas-power-plant-302254315.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20selected%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20design%20and%20build%20the%20carbon%20capture%20system%20for%20the%20Louisiana%20plant%20that%20Meta%20will%20help%20pay%20for.%20The%20project%2C%20at%20the%201-GW%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.entergy.com%2Fbrightfuturela%2Flakecharles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELake%20Charles%20power%20station%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20will%20cost%20around%20%241%20billion%20to%20build%2C%20Ashcroft%20said%2C%20who%20noted%20that%20a%20final%20cost%20estimate%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrescent%20Midstream%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20bidding%20to%20develop%20another%20utility-scale%20carbon%20capture%20system%20for%20a%20new%20gas%20plant%20that%20Entergy%20plans%20to%20build%20in%20Greenville%2C%20Mississippi%2C%20Ashcroft%20said.%20That%20station%20will%20help%20power%20a%20%2410%20billion%20data%20center%20campus%20nearby%20that%20Amazon%20announced%20in%20early%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20firm%20Carlyle%20Group%20acquired%20a%20majority%20stake%20in%20Crescent%20Midstream%2C%20a%20pipeline%20company%2C%20in%202021%2C%20and%20expanded%20it%20into%20the%20business%20of%20capturing%2C%20transporting%2C%20and%20sequestering%20carbon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAshcroft%20says%20that%20he%20anticipates%20Entergy%20will%20pursue%20at%20least%2010%20carbon%20capture%20projects%20across%20its%20portfolio%20in%20the%20near%20term.%20The%20Houston-based%20executive%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20the%20fossil%20fuel%20industry%20for%20years%2C%20said%20he%20has%20been%20astounded%20carbon%20capture's%20rapid%20recent%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoing%20from%202020%20to%202025%2C%20where%20now%20you're%20actually%20doing%20a%20project%2C%20yeah%2C%20it's%20pretty%20hard%20to%20imagine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220fac3956-41b4-49b1-ba62-8247529e698e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoaring%20energy%20demands%20and%20few%20carbon-free%20solutions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20interest%20in%20carbon%20capture%20lies%20an%20increasingly%20difficult%20array%20of%20choices%20in%20the%20nation's%20constrained%20energy%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faboutblaw.com%2FbgvW%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESome%20forecasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimate%20that%20more%20than%2090%20gigawatts%20of%20data%20center%20demand%20could%20be%20added%20to%20the%20grid%20nationally%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%E2%80%94the%20equivalent%20of%20about%20nine%20New%20York%20City-size%20blocks%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20center%20operators%20have%20sought%20out%20renewable%20sources%20of%20energy%20to%20curtail%20the%20enormous%20potential%20carbon%20footprint%20of%20all%20that%20capacity.%20Still%2C%20green%20options%2C%20including%20solar%20and%20wind%2C%20aren't%20considered%20reliable%20or%20intense%20enough%20to%20readily%20match%20the%20enormous%2C%20steady%20strains%20that%20the%20data%20facilities%20place%20on%20the%20grid%20day%20and%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%20new%20nuclear%20power%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20even%20more%20costly%20than%20capture%20and%20storage%20and%20fraught%20with%20labyrinthine%20regulatory%20hurdles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20meet%20the%20growing%20shortage%20of%20power%2C%20utilities%20have%20turned%20to%20an%20old%20asset%20in%20their%20portfolios%3A%20natural%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENatural-gas-fired%20generation%20capacity%20in%20the%20US%20has%20grown%20to%2079%20gigawatts%2C%20an%20increase%20of%2019%25%20since%202014%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eia.gov%2Ftodayinenergy%2Fdetail.php%3Fid%3D62163%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTotal%2520U.S.%2520natural%2520gas%252Dfired%2C59%2525%2520at%2520CCGT%2520power%2520plants.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Energy%20Information%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20as%20more%20solar%20and%20wind%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20grid%2C%20surging%20energy%20demand%20from%20data%20centers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spglobal.com%2Fratings%2Fen%2Fresearch%2Farticles%2F241022-data-centers-more-gas-will-be-needed-to-feed-u-s-growth-13290987%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20expected%20to%20drive%20more%20natural%20gas%20use%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20Virginia%2C%20Georgia%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20and%20South%20Carolina%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20utilities%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Futilities-ai-natural-gas-power-microsoft-meta-amazon-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanning%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20a%20combined%20total%20of%2020%20GW%20of%20new%20natural%20gas%20generation%2C%20primarily%20as%20a%20result%20of%20forecast%20data%20center%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20business%20model%20is%20we%20have%20to%20get%20the%20most%20power%2C%20quickest%20to%20stay%20out%20in%20front%20of%20the%20AI%20race%20as%20it%20were%2C%20gas%20must%20play%20a%20role%20in%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Erik%20Belz%2C%20the%20president%20and%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20the%20investment%20firm%20Engine%20No.%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngine%20No.%201%20is%20partnering%20with%20Chevron%20in%20its%20initiative%20to%20develop%20natural%20gas%20plants%20with%20a%20total%20capacity%20of%20about%204%20GW%20for%20energy%20customers%20constrained%20by%20the%20power%20shortage%2C%20including%20data%20centers.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20group%20also%20includes%20the%20energy%20equipment%20manufacturer%20GE%20Vernova%2C%20which%20is%20producing%20the%20turbines%20for%20the%20power%20plants.%20The%20venture%20plans%20to%20couple%20the%20facilities%20it%20builds%20with%20renewable%20energy%20sources%20and%20carbon%20capture%20to%20reduce%20their%20emissions.%20It%20expects%20to%20begin%20delivering%20the%20projects%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20is%20close%20to%20announcing%20its%20first%20deal%20with%20a%20data%20center%20customer%2C%20and%20that%20project%20may%20seek%20to%20harness%20carbon%20capture%2C%20Belz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20one%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a0e5faa-ec1f-4a3a-9dcc-736e9f9816da%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20web%20of%20technical%20hurdles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECarbon%20capture%20and%20storage%20come%20with%20myriad%20complications%20and%20uncertainties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%206%25%20of%20the%20exhaust%20fumes%20from%20a%20modern%20natural%20gas%20plant%20are%20composed%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20according%20to%20Ashcroft%2C%20the%20Crescent%20Midstream%20CEO.%20Huge%20absorbers%20filter%20that%20gas%20out%20before%20compressors%20liquify%20it.%20Pipelines%20transport%20the%20carbon%20to%20wells%20where%20it%20is%20pumped%20thousands%20of%20feet%20below%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lake%20Charles%20power%20station%2C%20where%20Crescent%20Midstream%20is%20planning%20its%20initial%20capture%20and%20storage%20project%2C%20is%20located%20on%20Louisiana's%20Gulf%20Coast%2C%20the%20seat%20of%20America's%20petroleum%20industry%20where%20there%20is%20an%20abundant%20network%20of%20pipelines%20and%20wells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAshcroft%20said%20the%20company%20would%20shove%20the%20gas%20as%20much%20as%2010%2C000%20feet%20below%20ground%20into%20saline%20beds%20beneath%20the%20gulf%20that%20lock%20in%20petroleum%20deposits%20and%20liquefied%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20geology%20and%20infrastructure%20don't%20exist%20widely%20across%20the%20US.%20It's%20not%20clear%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20whether%20carbon%20emissions%20could%20be%20as%20readily%20sequestered%20in%20northern%20Virginia%2C%20the%20country's%20largest%20data%20center%20market.%20Researchers%20at%20Virginia%20Tech%20are%20currently%20conducting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.vt.edu%2Farticles%2F2024%2F10%2Fscience_industrial_decarbonization.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeasibility%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20industrial%20carbon%20capture%20in%20the%20region%2C%20funded%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Fossil%20Energy%20and%20Carbon%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20questions%20whether%20the%20gas%2C%20once%20funneled%20below%20the%20earth%20will%20reliably%20remain%20there%20forever%20or%20if%20it%20could%20eventually%20seep%20out%20into%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20negating%20the%20whole%20enterprise%20and%20causing%20environmental%20harm.%20A%20large%20leak%20of%20methane%20gas%20from%20a%20storage%20well%20in%20California%20in%202015%20is%20considered%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fieefa.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2022-09%2FThe%2520Carbon%2520Capture%2520Crux.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworst%20greenhouse%20gas%20disaster%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20US%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20never%20been%20a%20carbon%20capture%20and%20storage%20unit%20operating%20at%20a%20gas-fired%20power%20plant%20in%20North%20America%20at%20the%20size%20that%20Big%20Tech%20would%20need%20to%20capture%20emissions%20from%20an%20AI%20data%20center%2C%20said%20Dennis%20Wamsted%2C%20energy%20analyst%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20Energy%20Economics%20and%20Financial%20Analysis%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20think%20tank%20that%20advocates%20for%20clean%20energy.%20%26quot%3BThat%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20can't%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Wamstead%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20would%20say%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20significantly%20more%20expensive%20than%20anything%20you've%20seen%20in%20a%20press%20release.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292a7f0ee-e1d7-45aa-a4ef-0f8da2b3c6a3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDifficult%20economics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20about%2051%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20carbon%20were%20captured%20in%202024%20out%20of%20a%20total%20global%20emissions%20output%20of%2040%20billion%20metric%20tons%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20a%20tenth%20of%20a%20percentage%20point%2C%20according%20to%20Pavel%20Molchanov%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Raymond%20James.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCarbon%20capture%20was%20a%20tiny%20niche%2C%26quot%3B%20Molchanov%20said.%20%26quot%3BSequestration%20will%20need%20to%20be%20available%20in%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20geographies%2C%20because%20guess%20what%2C%20not%20everybody%20lives%20next%20door%20to%20an%20oil%20field.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMolchanov%20said%20that%20capture%20and%20storage%20could%20be%20expanded%20by%20adapting%20more%20geologies%20in%20areas%20that%20might%20not%20otherwise%20accommodate%20sequestration.%20Of%20course%2C%20that%20might%20also%20increase%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22three%20mile%20island%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d5edb1ecd9784314b00b5c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThree%20Mile%20Island%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Ernst%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECapture%20and%20storage%20already%20faces%20difficult%20economics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20who%20sequester%20the%20carbon%20can%20receive%20an%20%2485%20federal%20tax%20credit%20for%20every%20metric%20ton%20of%20carbon%20captured%20and%20stored%2C%20which%20can%20be%20monetized%20in%20the%20corporate%20tax%20credit%20market%20to%20produce%20revenue.%20Ashcroft%20said%20that%20questions%20have%20persisted%20in%20the%20capture%20and%20storage%20business%20whether%20the%20credit%2C%20which%20was%20roughly%20doubled%20per%20metric%20ton%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20was%20sufficient%20to%20justify%20the%20steep%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20say%20you%20need%20%24120%20to%20make%20this%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAshcroft%20said%20he%20had%20an%20epiphany%20when%20he%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthree-mile-island-nuclear-plant-reopens-power-microsoft-ai-push-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft's%20announcement%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20September%20that%20it%20had%20reached%20a%20deal%20to%20revive%20a%20decommissioned%20reactor%20at%20the%20Three%20Mile%20Island%20nuclear%20station%20in%20Pennsylvania%20to%20provide%20it%20with%20carbon-free%20power%20for%20its%20data%20center%20operations.%20Ashcroft%20said%20that%20the%20hefty%20electricity%20premiums%20Microsoft%20agreed%20to%20as%20part%20of%20that%20deal%20were%20a%20clear%20signal%20that%20data%20center%20operators%20were%20%26quot%3Bwilling%20to%20pay%20more%20than%20market%20for%26quot%3B%20decarbonized%20energy%2C%20including%20capture%20and%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20tax%20credits%20alone%20aren't%20enough%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20Lake%20Charles%20sequestration%20project%2C%20the%20deal%20will%20rely%20on%20Meta%2C%20which%20has%20agreed%20to%20pay%20a%20rider%2C%20up%20to%20a%20fixed%20amount%2C%20on%20its%20utility%20bill%20with%20Entergy%20in%20Louisiana%20to%20offset%20the%20costs.%20A%20spokeswoman%20for%20Meta%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMolchanov%20agrees%20that%20capture%20and%20storage%20is%20poised%20to%20grow.%20He%20projects%20that%20the%20amount%20of%20carbon%20sequestered%20annually%20will%20quadruple%20by%202030%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%20data%20center%20demand%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20earnings%20call%20in%20late%20January%2C%20Exxon%20Mobil%20executives%20said%20that%20their%20carbon%20capture%20and%20storage%20operations%20and%20a%20related%20business%20producing%20low-emissions%20hydrogen%20with%20capture%20and%20storage%20technology%20could%20generate%20%242%20billion%20of%20annual%20revenue%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20pretty%20aggressive%20growth%20plans%20in%20this%20space%2C%26quot%3BExxon%20Mobil's%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fool.com%2Fearnings%2Fcall-transcripts%2F2025%2F01%2F31%2Fexxonmobil-xom-q4-2024-earnings-call-transcript%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDarren%20Woods%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20the%20call%2C%20according%20to%20a%20transcript%20by%20The%20Motley%20Fool.%20%26quot%3BBut%20again%2C%20all%20dependent%20upon%20customer%20interest%20and%20customers'%20willingness%20to%20engage%20in%20long-term%20contracts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetty%20Jiang%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Barclays%20who%20covers%20Exxon%20Mobil%20said%20that%20she%20believed%20the%20company%20would%20only%20trumpet%20the%20business%20of%20capture%20and%20storage%20if%20it%20had%20received%20interest%20from%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20stay%20tuned%20on%20exactly%20what%20these%20investments%20look%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20Jiang%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20will%20be%20raising%20their%20capital%20in%20these%20areas%20and%20saying%20what%20they're%20saying%20about%20the%20market%20opportunities%20if%20they%20are%20not%20having%20the%20conversation%20in%20the%20background%20to%20really%20give%20them%20the%20confidence%20that%20it%20is%20indeed%20an%20area%20of%20growth%20for%20Exxon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-energy-demand-carbon-capture-meta-exxon-chevron-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740045602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4dcdeeb4be2fff9a4ea2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2