Indian%20women%2C%20often%20overlooked%20due%20to%20misconceptions%20associating%20it%20more%20with%20men.%20Symptoms%20in%20women%20can%20include%20chest%20pain%2C%20fatigue%2C%20and%20lightheadedness%2C%20and%20emotional%20stress%20can%20trigger%20attacks.%20Awareness%20of%20risk%20factors%2C%20healthy%20lifestyles%2C%20and%20treatment%20options%20like%20Cardiac%20Resynchronization%20Therapy%20are%20essential.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20LIFESTYLE%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Is%20Bollywood%20Only%20About%20'Reels'%20And%20'Memes'%20Now%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBollywood%20has%20long%20lost%20the%20art%20of%20song%20picturisation.%20It%20feels%20like%20an%20eternity%20since%20any%20track%20was%20filmed%20with%20flair%2C%20with%20imagination.%20It%20feels%20like%20even%20longer%20since%20songs%20were%20known%20for%20their%20shot-taking%2C%20for%20what%20they%20conveyed%20visually.%20Now%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20traditionalists%20(Karan%20Johar%2C%20Sanjay%20Leela%20Bhansali)%2C%20still%20hold%20on%20to%20its%20magic.%20Some%20have%20long%20surrendered%20it%20to%20narrative%20potency.%20Others%20don't%20even%20pause%20to%20grasp%20the%20weight%20of%20what's%20been%20lost%E2%80%94the%20way%20song%20and%20dance%20once%20breathed%20life%20into%20Bombay%20cinema%2C%20the%20way%20they%20turned%20emotion%20into%20something%20tangible%2C%20something%20immortal.%20No%20wonder%20they%20are%20used%2C%20if%20at%20all%2C%20as%20afterthoughts%3A%20devoid%20of%20purpose%2C%20robbed%20of%20poetry.%20Even%20fillers%20are%20rare%20now%2C%20as%20at%20least%20some%20of%20those%20once%20had%20the%20grandeur%20of%20a%20music%20video.%20Now%2C%20songs%20are%20shot%20not%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20but%20to%20be%20scrolled%20past.%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20shot%20only%20as%20reels%E2%80%94designed%20not%20to%20live%20in%20memory%2C%20but%20to%20chase%20algorithms%2C%20not%20to%20move%20hearts%2C%20but%20to%20rank%20higher%20on%20a%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20Bow%20To%20Algorithm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20algorithm%20dictates%20its%20grammar.%20The%20hook%20line%20is%20the%20heartbeat%3B%20the%20rest%20dissolves%20into%20oblivion.%20Composers%20no%20longer%20create%20melodies%20that%20linger%3B%20they%20engineer%20earworms%20designed%20to%20vanish%20as%20quickly%20as%20they%20arrive.%20Verses%20surrender%20to%20viral%20loops.%20The%20picturisation%20follows%20suit.%20The%20hook%20step%20is%20everywhere%2C%20the%20rest%20a%20blur.%20Long%20takes%20are%20sacrificed%20at%20the%20altar%20of%20attention.%20Slow%20dissolves%20give%20way%20to%20jump%20cuts.%20Movements%20are%20choreographed%20not%20for%20the%20screen%20but%20for%20the%20scroll.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Tauba%20Tauba%2C'%20%E2%80%98Lutt%20Putt%20Gaya%2C'%20%E2%80%98Aayi%20Nayi'%20are%20a%20few%20songs%20known%20not%20for%20their%20feeling%2C%20their%20flow%2C%20but%20for%20a%20step.%20Does%20anyone%20remember%20what%20comes%20before%20or%20after%3F%20Similarly%2C%20%E2%80%98Pehli%20Bhi%20Main%2C'%20%E2%80%98Aabaad%20Bardbaad%2C'%20%E2%80%98Sajni%2C'%20%E2%80%98Mera%20Dholna'%20have%20their%20scratches%20fill%20the%20feed%20in%20fractured%20bursts.%20But%20does%20anyone%20remember%20them%20beyond%20their%20%3Cem%3Emukhda%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20a%20song%2C%20if%20not%20memorised%20by%20heart%2C%20was%20at%20least%20known%20by%20the%20soul.%20Hook%20steps%20have%20always%20found%20a%20place%20in%20the%20mind%2C%20but%20once%2C%20the%20space%2C%20the%20craft%2C%20the%20poetry%20of%20how%20a%20song%20was%20filmed%20mattered%20just%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EViral%20Fever%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20matters%20is%20how%20to%20conquer%20reels%2C%20and%20in%20its%20wake%2C%20a%20new%20phenomenon%20has%20emerged%3A%20reelification.%20Everything%20is%20filtered%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20a%20social%20media%20reel%2C%20designed%20with%20its%20rhythm%20in%20mind%2C%20shaped%20to%20fit%20its%20fading%20frame%2C%20measured%20not%20by%20artistry%20but%20by%20virality.%20And%20the%20first%2C%20greatest%20casualty%3F%20Song%20and%20dance.%20This%20isn't%20to%20dismiss%20the%20craft%20of%20making%20a%20reel%3B%20it%20has%20its%20own%20language%2C%20its%20own%20grammar.%20But%20there's%20a%20case%20to%20be%20made%20about%20how%20it%20has%20redefined%20the%20way%20spectators%20consume%20cinema%E2%80%94nay%2C%20%E2%80%98content'.%20Gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20songs%20were%20reborn%20through%20remakes.%20Now%2C%20they%20are%20resurrected%20on%20feeds%2C%20removed%20of%20context%2C%20repurposed%20into%20trends.%20Gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20a%20song%20belonged%20to%20a%20singular%20moment.%20Now%2C%20they%20are%20plastered%20over%20anything%20and%20everything%2C%20devoid%20of%20meaning%2C%20detached%20from%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20also%20led%20to%20moments%20of%20ingenuity%2C%20flashes%20of%20creative%20flourish.%20It%20has%20opened%20ears%20to%20forgotten%20melodies%20and%20introduced%20fresh%20sounds%20to%20unfamiliar%20audiences.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20speaks%20to%20the%20potency%20of%20reelification%20when%20an%20Iranian%20dirge%20of%20enslavement%2C%20%E2%80%98Jamal%20Kudu'%2C%20becomes%20the%20heartbeat%20of%20a%20thousand%20edits%2C%20or%20when%20the%20ghost%20of%20Laxmikant-Pyarelal's%20%E2%80%98Ek%20Hasina%20Thi'%20finds%20an%20afterlife%20in%20the%20digital%20cosmos.%20But%20the%20greatest%20casualty%20of%20all%20is%20the%20dwindling%20attention%20span%20of%20the%20viewer.%20Everything%20must%20be%20immediate%3A%20sharp%2C%20urgent%2C%20catchy.%20There%20is%20no%20room%20for%20hesitation%2C%20no%20patience%20for%20the%20slow%20bloom%20of%20meaning.%20A%20song%2C%20a%20scene%2C%20a%20film%20has%20only%20one%20chance%20to%20grip%2C%20to%20stun%2C%20to%20seize.%20It%20must%20be%20packaged%20in%20an%20aesthetic%20that%20conforms%2C%20because%20anything%20else%20is%20not%20arresting%20enough.%20Things%20must%20be%20said%20quickly%2C%20or%20not%20at%20all.%20Slow%20burn%20is%20a%20crime%2C%20subtlety%20a%20sin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDitch%20The%20Slow%20Burn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20stories%20that%20find%20favour%20in%20the%20last%20half%20a%20decade.%20Whether%20in%20long-form%20storytelling%20or%20theatrical%20releases%2C%20patterns%20emerge%20in%20genres%20that%20get%20the%20green%20light%20while%20others%20fade%20into%20the%20background.%20There%20are%2C%20of%20course%2C%20many%20reasons%E2%80%94star%20vanity%20being%20one%E2%80%94but%20shrinking%20attention%20spans%20remains%20the%20most%20decisive%20one.%20Take%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20OTT%20space.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20it%20is%20replete%20with%20crime%20thrillers%20and%20police%20procedurals.%20It%20isn't%20a%20mere%20coincidence.%20These%20genres%20thrive%20on%20urgency%2C%20on%20the%20illusion%20of%20high%20stakes.%20They%20grip%20the%20audience%20with%20turns%2C%20sustain%20their%20hold%20with%20twists%2C%20and%20hit%20them%20back%20with%20a%20sudden%20death%20or%20two.%20And%20if%20all%20else%20fails%2C%20there's%20always%20the%20safety%20net%20of%20a%20cliffhanger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheatrical%20cinema%2C%20too%2C%20has%20narrowed%20its%20focus%2C%20with%20only%20a%20select%20few%20genres%20gaining%20traction.%20One%20such%20breed%20is%20horror-comedy.%20It%20is%20not%20simply%20comedy%20that%20captivates.%20It's%20the%20flashes%20of%20horror%20that%20keep%20the%20audience%20hooked%2C%20leaning%20forward%2C%20ready%20for%20whatever's%20next.%20These%20films%20thrive%20on%20contrasts%2C%20where%20punchlines%20are%20often%20accompanied%20by%20the%20suddenness%20of%20a%20shock.%20Similarly%2C%20mass%20action%20films%20have%20evolved%2C%20distancing%20themselves%20from%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98masala'%20tradition.%20Payoff%20after%20payoff%2C%20punchline%20after%20punchline%E2%80%94strung%20together%20like%20a%20highlight%20reel.%20Filmmakers%20like%20Atlee%20(%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EBaby%20John%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20Shankar%20(%3Cem%3EGame%20Changer%3C%2Fem%3E)%20now%20work%20in%20a%20world%20where%20tension%20takes%20a%20backseat%20to%20the%20GIF-able%20moment%2C%20where%20the%20thrill%20lies%20in%20instant%20gratification%2C%20not%20in%20the%20art%20of%20build-up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20argued%20that%20both%20these%20filmmakers%20hail%20from%20a%20South%20Indian%20tradition%2C%20where%20mass%20cinema%20has%20long%20followed%20its%20own%20distinctive%20identity%2C%20far%20removed%20from%20Bollywood's%20usual%20syntax.%20True%20as%20this%20may%20be%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20Bollywood%2C%20too%2C%20has%20slipped%20into%20this%20very%20pattern.%20Films%20now%20often%20resemble%20reels%20dressed%20as%20cinema%3A%20moments%20of%20enjoyment%20come%20only%20when%20everything%20rushes%20forward%2C%20when%20chaos%20is%20the%20currency%2C%20and%20everything%20is%20hurled%20at%20the%20screen%20with%20a%20hope%20that%20something%2C%20anything%2C%20will%20connect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmbrace%20The%20Absurd%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20%3Cem%3EBadass%20Ravi%20Kumar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20starring%20Himesh%20Reshammiya%20in%20the%20titular%20role.%20From%20the%20outset%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20pastiche%20that%20knows%20exactly%20how%20to%20laugh%20at%20itself.%20Yet%2C%20it%20isn't%20that%20self-aware%2C%20that%20meta%20enough%20to%20mock%20the%20trends.%20Rather%2C%20it%20surrenders%20to%20them%2C%20wearing%20its%20absurdity%20proudly.%20The%20writing%2C%20the%20framing%2C%20the%20acting%E2%80%94all%20drip%20with%20an%20almost%20deliberate%20excess%2C%20as%20though%20every%20dialogue%20is%20a%20competition%20to%20out-cheese%20the%20last%2C%20every%20moment%20a%20louder%20declaration%20of%20its%20own%20implausibility.%20Stakes%20rise%20relentlessly%2C%20timelines%20blur%20in%20an%20endless%20loop%2C%20and%20the%20action%20is%20served%20with%20the%20perfect%20spoonful%20of%20corn.%20It%20isn't%20quite%20cringe%2C%20but%20something%20else%20altogether%3A%20a%20performance%20for%20an%20audience%20that%20are%20in%20on%20the%20joke%2C%20laughing%20both%20with%20and%20at%20the%20spectacle%2C%20a%20strange%20fusion%20of%20reel%20cinema%20and%20meme%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20surge%20in%20re-releases%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20Hindi%20Cinema%2C%20owes%20much%20of%20its%20momentum%20to%20the%20algorithm.%20Look%20closely%2C%20and%20you'll%20see%20a%20pattern%3A%20the%20films%20that%20have%20been%20re-released%2C%20the%20ones%20that%20have%20drawn%20massive%20crowds%2C%20are%20those%20that%20have%20long%20been%20favoured%20by%20the%20reels.%20This%20isn't%20to%20suggest%20they%20lack%20the%20weight%20of%20icon%20status%2C%20or%20to%20dismiss%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20of%20the%20audiences%20flocking%20to%20these%20screenings%20have%20never%20experienced%20them%20in%20a%20packed%20theater.%20But%20it's%20undeniable%20that%20these%20films%2C%20often%20propelled%20by%20viral%20scenes%20and%20songs%2C%20have%20been%20resurrected%20on%20feeds%2C%20feeding%20the%20collective%20nostalgia%20of%20the%20internet.%20Say%2C%20%3Cem%3ELaila%20Majnu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20%3Cem%3ESanam%20Teri%20Kasam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20barely%20registered%20when%20they%20first%20released.%20But%20today%2C%20they%20command%20the%20attention%20of%20thousands%20of%20audiences%2C%20filling%20theaters%20across%20the%20country.%20Their%20popularity%20is%20no%20longer%20bound%20to%20their%20original%20release%20but%20reborn%20through%20the%20endless%20loops%20of%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Will%20Be%20Remembered%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20film%20promotions%2C%20arguably%20the%20one%20arena%20where%20Hindi%20producers%20used%20to%20readily%20pour%20their%20creativity%20and%20money%2C%20have%20now%20been%20surrendered%20to%20the%20scroll.%20No%20more%20whirlwind%20city%20tours%2C%20no%20more%20interviews%20where%20actors%20could%20build%20a%20lasting%20connection%20with%20their%20audience.%20Now%2C%20virality%20is%20the%20only%20currency.%20A%20press%20conference%20isn't%20a%20conversation%3B%20it's%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20memes.%20A%20song%20release%20isn't%20about%20melody%20or%20emotion%3B%20it's%20about%20the%20challenge%20it%20sparks%3A%20who%20can%20master%20the%20hook%20step%2C%20who%20can%20twist%20it%20into%20something%20clickable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ELoveyapa%20%3C%2Fem%3Etitle%20track%20isn't%20being%20performed%20by%20actors%20but%20perfected%20by%20influencers.%20Celebrities%20no%20longer%20seek%20out%20journalists%3B%20they%20sit%20across%20viral%20podcasters%20who%20trade%20depth%20for%20reach.%20And%20Veer%20Pahariya%20isn't%20a%20name%20on%20people's%20lips%20because%20of%20his%20craft%E2%80%94he%20is%20a%20construct%20shaped%20by%20the%20internet's%20endless%20need%20to%20turn%20anything%20and%20everything%20into%20conversation.%20Because%2C%20after%20all%2C%20reelification%20is%20not%20just%20a%20trend%E2%80%94it%20is%20an%20evolution%2C%20an%20omnipresent%20force%20shaping%20cinema's%20contours.%20It%20is%20the%20new%20language%2C%20the%20new%20currency%2C%20the%20new%20reality.%20And%20in%20this%20reality%2C%20the%20algorithm%20reigns%20supreme%2C%20dictating%20what%20survives%2C%20what%20fades%2C%20and%20what%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20will%20ever%20be%20remembered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anas%20Arif%20is%20a%20film%20writer%20and%20a%20media%20graduate%20from%20AJKMCRC%2C%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740045060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%