3A%22Legal%20experts%20weigh%20in%20on%20Delta's%20%2430%2C000%20'no%20strings%20attached'%20payment%20to%20passengers%20after%20crash-landing%20incident%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%20plane%20upside%20down%20on%20snowy%20tarmac%2C%20without%20its%20wings.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b69c23eb4be2fff9a51335%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221466%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%20plane%20that%20crashed%20at%20Toronto%20Pearson%20International%20Airport.%3Cp%3ETransportation%20Safety%20Board%2Fvia%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDelta%20is%20giving%20%2430%2C000%20to%20every%20passenger%20who%20was%20on%20the%20flight%20that%20crash-landed%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDelta%20could%20still%20be%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20more%20damages%20if%20passengers%20sue.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAll%2080%20people%20on%20board%20survived%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-premium-seats-economy-cabin-profit-investor-day-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelta%20Air%20Lines%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20it%20will%20be%20giving%20%2430%2C000%20to%20every%20passenger%20who%20was%20on%20board%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-flight-upside-down-toronto-airport-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflight%20that%20flipped%20upside%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20landed%20in%20Toronto%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Durrant%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Delta%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bgesture%20has%20no%20strings%20attached%20and%20does%20not%20affect%20rights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20when%20and%20how%20passengers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20claim%20the%20money%20from%20Delta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegal%20experts%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20Delta's%20payout%20is%20an%20act%20of%20goodwill%2C%20the%20airline%20could%20be%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20further%20damages%20if%20passengers%20choose%20to%20sue%20for%20more%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20%2430%2C000%20advance%20payment%20offer%20by%20Delta%20is%20a%20good%20start%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20as%20long%20as%20passengers%20do%20not%20have%20to%20give%20up%20any%20of%20their%20rights%20for%20full%20and%20fair%20compensation%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robert%20Hedrick%2C%20an%20aviation%20accident%20attorney%20from%20the%20Seattle-based%20Aviation%20Law%20Group.%20Hedrick%20is%20taking%20passenger%20cases%20from%20the%20Delta%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20R.%20Applebaum%2C%20an%20aviation%20accident%20attorney%20in%20New%20York%2C%20said%20such%20payments%20are%20%26quot%3Bfairly%20typical%20in%20major%20aviation%20accidents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplebaum%20and%20Hedrick%20said%20passengers%20should%20consult%20with%20an%20aviation%20attorney%20before%20accepting%20the%20money%20to%20ensure%20it%20comes%20with%20no%20strings%20attached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20attorneys%20said%20Delta's%20payout%20isn't%20taxable%20under%20US%20law%2C%20though%20Hedrick%20said%20there%20might%20be%20some%20exceptions%20depending%20on%20the%20circumstance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20Flight%204819%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20operated%20by%20Delta's%20subsidiary%2C%20Endeavor%20Air%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-crash-toronto-plane-upside-down-airline-pilots-experts-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrash-landed%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Toronto%20Pearson%20International%20Airport%20on%20Monday.%20The%20flight%20from%20Minneapolis%20was%20carrying%2076%20passengers%20and%20four%20crew%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%2080%20people%20on%20board%20survived.%20The%20wreckage%20of%20the%20plane%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20airport%20on%20Wednesday%20ev