20With%20more%20than%2010%20million%20users%20eagerly%20waiting%2C%20they%20will%20soon%20be%20able%20to%20migrate%20their%20mined%20Pi%20coins%20from%20the%20testnet%20to%20the%20mainnet.%20This%20milestone%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20Pi%20Coin's%20transition%20into%20a%20tradable%20asset%2C%20sparking%20a%20worldwide%20craze%20that%20spans%20countries%20like%20Iran%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Indonesia.%20As%20the%20official%20listing%20draws%20near%2C%20the%20excitement%20surrounding%20Pi%20Coin%20continues%20to%20grow%20exponentially%2C%20leaving%20many%20users%20hopeful%20for%20potential%20profit%20and%20widespread%20adoption.%20Let's%20have%20a%20look%20at%20the%20details%20of%20the%20Pi%20Coin%20listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Pi%20Network%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fdigital-assets%2Farticle%2Fwhat-is-pi-network%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Forbes%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pi%20Network%20is%20a%20blockchain%20project%20that%20lets%20users%20mine%20cryptocurrency%20through%20a%20mobile%20app.%20Started%20in%202019%20by%20Stanford%20graduates%2C%20the%20project%20aims%20to%20make%20crypto%20accessible%20to%20everyday%20people%20without%20specialised%20hardware%20or%20technical%20knowledge.%20Unlike%20Bitcoin%2C%20which%20requires%20expensive%20mining%20equipment%2C%20Pi%20can%20be%20earned%20by%20verifying%20presence%20on%20a%20phone%20app%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20the%20Live%20Price%20of%20Pi%20Coin%20Here%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20market%20data%2C%20Pi%20Coin%20is%20currently%20trading%20at%20%241.78%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.okx.com%2Fprice%2Fpi-network-pi%5C%22%3EOKX%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20successful%20launch%20of%20its%20mainnet%20at%208%3A30%20am%20UTC%20on%20February%2020.%20Additionally%2C%20Pi%20Coin%20is%20trading%20at%20%241.70%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bitget.site%2Fprice%2Fpi-network%5C%22%3EBitget%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20of%20the%20time%20of%20this%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Pi%20Network%20Works%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fdigital-assets%2Farticle%2Fwhat-is-pi-network%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pi%20uses%20the%20Stellar%20Consensus%20Protocol%20instead%20of%20Bitcoin's%20energy-intensive%20proof%20of%20work%20system.%20Users%20build%20trust%20circles%20by%20nominating%203-5%20reliable%20contacts%2C%20creating%20an%20interconnected%20web%20of%20verified%20members.%20These%20connections%20form%20a%20global%20trust%20graph%20that%20helps%20secure%20the%20network%20and%20validate%20transactions%20without%20massive%20computing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mining%20process%20rewards%20different%20types%20of%20contributions.%20Pioneers%20earn%20base%20rewards%20for%20daily%20check-ins%2C%20additional%20amounts%20for%20growing%20their%20trusted%20circles%20and%20bonuses%20for%20running%20full%20nodes%20on%20computers.%20The%20network%20also%20incentivises%20app%20usage%20and%20Pi%20lockups%20to%20support%20ecosystem%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPioneers%2C%20Open%20Network%20will%20launch%20at%208am%20UTC%20on%20February%2020%2C%202025!%20With%20millions%20of%20KYC-verified%20Pioneers%20and%20a%20thriving%20utilities-driven%20ecosystem%2C%20Open%20Network%20expands%20available%20opportunities%2C%20which%20allows%20Pioneers%20to%20connect%20Pi%20with%20external%20systems%20for%20use%20in%20real-world%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAdpXNhpcUD%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAdpXNhpcUD%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Pi%20Network%20(%40PiCoreTeam)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPiCoreTeam%2Fstatus%2F1889445244464517293%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2011%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20December%202021%2C%20Pi%20has%20operated%20on%20its%20Mainnet%20blockchain%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Benclosed%26quot%3B%20period.%20During%20this%20phase%2C%20users%20must%20complete%20know%20your%20customer%20verification%20to%20transfer%20their%20mined%20Pi%20to%20the%20blockchain.%20The%20project%20plans%20to%20remove%20these%20restrictions%20in%20its%20%26quot%3Bopen%20network%26quot%3B%20phase%2C%20allowing%20full%20external%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20a%20concise%20breakdown%20of%20how%20to%20acquire%20Pi%20Coin%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDownload%20%26amp%3B%20Install%3A%20Get%20the%20Pi%20Network%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStart%20Mining%3A%20Tap%20the%20lightning%20bolt%20icon%20to%20begin%20earning%20Pi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBuild%20Security%20Circle%3A%20After%203%20days%2C%20add%203-5%20trusted%20contacts%20to%20boost%20your%20mining%20rate.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERefer%20Friends%3A%20Share%20your%20referral%20code%20to%20increase%20earnings.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApp%20Engagement%3A%20Participate%20in%20app%20features%20like%20chats%20and%20polls.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnderstand%20Roles%3A%20Learn%20about%20Pioneer%2C%20Contributor%2C%20and%20Ambassador%20roles%20to%20maximize%20your%20earning%20potential.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740042480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ff4dhi33o_pi-network_625x300_20_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fpi-coin-listing-today-what-it-is-price-guide-and-steps-to-own-it-7752875%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pi%20Coin's%20mainnet%20launch%20is%20finally%20underway%2C%20and%20the%20global%20interest%20in%20the%20cryptocurrency%20is%20surging%2C%20with%20millions%20of%20users%20ready%20to%20migrate%20their%20mined%20coins%20for%20trading.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%