%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Follow%20Code%20Of%20Ethics%3A%20Centre%20To%20OTT%20Platforms%20Amid%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20channels%20and%20OTT%20websites%20were%20warned%20Thursday%20to%20follow%20the%20Code%20of%20Ethics%20prescribed%20in%20the%20IT%20Rules%20(2021)%20and%20ensure%20critical%20self-regulation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20implement%20%26quot%3Baccess%20control%20for%20'A'%20rated%20content%26quot%3B%20to%20avoid%20children%20consuming%20inappropriate%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20from%20the%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Ministry%20comes%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20'obscene'%20remarks%20made%20by%20podcaster%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Franveer-allahbadia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERanveer%20Allahbadia%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20an%20episode%20of%20stand-up%20comedy%20show%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Findias-got-latent-row%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia's%20Got%20Latent%3C%2Fa%3E'.%20The%20episode%20in%20question%20was%20on%20YouTube%20till%20the%20government%20ordered%20its%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20stated%20it%20had%20received%20complaints%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bspread%20of%20obscene%2C%20pornographic%2C%20and%20vulgar%20content%20by%20certain%20publishers%20of%20online%20curated%20content%20(OTT%20platforms)%20and%20social%20media%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20stressed%20that%20the%20law%20requires%20OTT%20platforms%20to%20%26quot%3Bnot%20transmit%20any%20content%20which%20is%20prohibited%20by%20law%20(and)%20undertake%20age-based%20classification%20of%20content%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20the%20Rules%20provide%20that%20self-regulatory%20bodies%20of%20OTT%20platforms%20shall%20oversee%20and%20ensure%20alignment%20and%20adherence%20by%20the%20OTT%20platforms%20to%20the%20Code%20of%20Ethics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notification%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20above%20it%20is%20advised%20OTT%20platforms%20adhere%20to%20various%20provisions%20of%20applicable%20laws%2C%20and%20Code%20of%20Ethics%20prescribed%20under%20IT%20Rules%2C%202021%20while%20publishing%20content%20on%20platforms%2C%20including%20stricter%20adherence%20of%20age-based%20classification%20of%20content%20prescribed%20under%20Code%20of%20Ethics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notification%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20also%20followed%20sharp%20questions%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20this%20week%2C%20as%20it%20heard%20a%20plea%20by%20Mr%20Allahbadia%20to%20club%20the%20police%20cases%20(two%2C%20so%20far)%20that%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20Justice%20N%20Kotiswar%20Singh%20came%20down%20hard%20on%20Mr%20Allahbadia%2C%20also%20known%20as%20'BeerBiceps%20guy'%20on%20Instagram%2C%20for%20his%20comment%20about%20parents%20and%20sex%2C%20and%20asked%20the%20centre%20if%20it%20is%20planning%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20regulate%20%26quot%3Bobscene%26quot%3B%20content%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franveer-allahbadia-case-in-supreme-court-just-because-you-are-popular-supreme-court-to-ranveer-allahbadia-7736130%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDirt%20On%20Mind%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%20Relief%20But%20Scathing%20Rebuke%20For%20Allahbadia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20it%20would%20not%20%26quot%3Bleave%20a%20vacuum%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20would%20take%20action%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnion%20of%20India%20is%20a%20party...%20We%20would%20like%20to%20do%20something.%20Government%20of%20India%20will%20willingly%20do%20it%2C%20we%20will%20be%20very%20happy.%20Otherwise%2C%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20leave%20this%20vacuum.%20The%20way%20it%20is%20being%20misused%20by%20so-called%20YouTube%20channels...%20we%20have%20issued%20notice...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-seeks-centres-response-over-pornographic-content-on-youtube-social-media-amid-ranveer-allahbadia-row-7736525%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWon't%20Leave%20Vacuum%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20On%20'Obscene'%20Content%20Online%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20court's%20questions%20to%20the%20centre%2C%20a%20parliamentary%20panel%20had%20asked%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20to%20submit%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-youtuber-ranveer-allahbadia-row-house-panel-writes-to-it-ministry-on-digital-content-laws-7747696%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enote%20on%20the%20efficacy%20of%20existing%20laws%20in%20dealing%20with%20such%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20suggest%20amendments%20needed%20to%20bring%20online%20platforms%20under%20required%20legal%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740039000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fkd2rsoa8_ranveer-allahbadia_625x300_10_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffollow-code-of-ethics-centre-to-ott-platforms-amid-indias-got-latent-row-7752769%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Social%20media%20channels%20and%20OTT%20sites%20were%20warned%20to%20follow%20the%20Code%20of%20Ethics%20prescribed%20in%20the%20IT%20Rules%20(2021)%20and%20ensure%20critical%20self-regulation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20implement%20%26quot%3Baccess%20control%20for%20'A'%20rated%20content%26quot%3B%20to%20avoid%20children%20consuming%20such%20content.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffollow-code-of-ethics-centre-to-ott-platforms-amid-indias-got-latent-row-7752769%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20budget%202025-26%3A%20AI%20city%2C%20cyber%20security%20park%20and%20more%3B%20see%20key%20details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740038745000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118411645%2Cimgsize-33370.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fup-budget-2025-26-ai-city-cyber-security-park-and-more-see-key-details%2Farticleshow%2F118411568.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Khanna%20presented%20a%20Rs%208%2C08%2C736-crore%20Budget%20for%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20focusing%20on%20research%2C%20development%2C%20and%20Information%20Technology%20for%202025-26.%20Major%20allocations%20include%2022%25%20for%20development%2C%2013%25%20for%20education%2C%20and%20significant%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20City%20and%20'Zero%20Poverty%20Abhiyan.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fup-budget-2025-26-ai-city-cyber-security-park-and-more-see-key-details%2Farticleshow%2F118411568.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Congress%20Reshuffle%3A%20Rahul%20Chooses%20His%20Friends%2C%20But%20Can%20They%20Deliver%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20it%20changes%2C%20the%20more%20it%20remains%20the%20same.%20The%20Congress%20has%20carried%20out%20a%20long-delayed%20but%20a%20seemingly%20half-hearted%20reshuffle%20in%20the%20party%20secretariat.%20Ironically%2C%20it%20comes%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20defeats%20in%20state%20polls.%20Only%20two%20general%20secretaries%20have%20been%20added%20and%20a%20few%20in-charges%20for%20various%20states%20have%20been%20replaced.%20The%20million-dollar%20question%20is%2C%20can%20this%20team%20strengthen%20the%20hands%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20going%20through%20a%20rough%20patch%20after%20being%20at%20his%20peak%20in%20June%20last%20year%20as%20his%20party%20secured%2099%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFriends%20In%20Right%20Places%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20apparent%20in%20the%20new%20order%3A%20Gandhi%20has%20tried%20to%20stitch%20up%20his%20own%20trusted%20team%2C%20bringing%20to%20the%20fore%20several%20associates%20who%20had%20been%20working%20with%20him%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20A%20complaint%20with%20Gandhi%20had%20been%20that%20he%20often%20failed%20to%20carry%20the%20party%20with%20him%3B%20some%20observers%20even%20insist%20that%20he%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20two%20separate%20entities.%20Now%2C%20with%20his%20own%20men%20firmly%20in%20place%2C%20that%20perception%20might%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20many%20of%20the%20new%20entrants%20are%20leaders%20who%20represent%20disadvantaged%20or%20minority%20sections.%20Former%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20has%20been%20appointed%20the%20new%20general%20secretary%20of%20Punjab%2C%20while%20Syed%20Naseer%20Hussain%2C%20also%20appointed%20general%20secretary%2C%20will%20handle%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh.%20Former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20chief%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Lallu%20is%20the%20new%20in-charge%20of%20Odisha%2C%20while%20B.K.%20Hariprasad%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20veteran%20at%20the%20AICC%20Secretariat%20and%20has%20handled%20many%20states%20in%20various%20capacities%2C%20has%20been%20given%20the%20charge%20of%20Haryana%2C%20a%20tricky%20territory.%20Saptagiri%20Sankar%20Ulaka%20will%20handle%20Manipur%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Tripura%20and%20Nagaland.%20He%20is%20the%20only%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20of%20the%20party%20from%20Odisha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Meenakshi%20Natrajan%20has%20been%20made%20in%20charge%20of%20Telangana%2C%20while%20K.%20Raju%2C%20the%20national%20coordinator%20of%20the%20party's%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20OBC%2C%20and%20Minorities%20cell%2C%20is%20the%20new%20in-charge%20of%20Jharkhand.%20Krishna%20Allavaru%20has%20been%20handed%20Bihar%2C%20and%20Girish%20Chodankar%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Puducherry.%20Finally%2C%20senior%20leader%20Rajni%20Patil%20has%20been%20given%20the%20charge%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Chandigarh%2C%20and%20Harish%20Chaudhary%20has%20been%20made%20in-charge%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWheels%20Within%20Wheels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20this%20reshuffle%20change%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20Congress%3F%20That's%20debatable.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20grand%20old%20party%2C%20there%20are%20wheels%20within%20wheels%2C%20and%20the%20organisation%20cannot%20be%20run%20without%20the%20first%20family%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat.%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20might%20be%20the%20Congress%20President%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20organisation%2C%20the%20man%20who%20runs%20the%20show%20is%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20the%20General%20Secretary%20(Organisation)%20and%20the%20blue-eyed%20boy%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20might%20also%20be%20one%20of%20the%20general%20secretaries%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20her%20stature%20is%20much%20more%20than%20that%2C%20though%20her%20exact%20role%20in%20the%20new%20scheme%20of%20things%20is%20still%20unclear.%20The%20issue%20of%20accountability%20has%20hardly%20bothered%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20in%20the%20new%20appointments%2C%20the%20talk%20is%20that%20the%20old%20guard%20has%20been%20ignored%20because%20Gandhi%20was%20not%20very%20comfortable%20with%20leaders%20who%20have%20been%20senior%20in%20age%20and%20experience.%20The%20appointment%20of%20Kharge%20two%20years%20ago%20is%20another%20story.%20Those%20changes%20took%20place%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20gasping%20and%20wanted%20a%20drastic%20overhaul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Serious%20Is%20Congress%20About%20Bihar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20things%20stand%20out%20in%20the%20new%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20the%20party%20had%20lost%20Chhattisgarh%20when%20Baghel%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20also%20couldn't%20improve%20its%20state%20tally%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20under%20his%20leadership.%20He%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20recent%20Maharashtra%20elections%20too%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20again%20failed.%20Now%2C%20ironically%2C%20he%20has%20been%20given%20charge%20of%20Punjab%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%20and%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20would%20work%20hard%20to%20stop%20the%20Congress's%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20Bihar.%20It%20is%20another%20key%20poll-bound%20state%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%2C%20a%20junior%20player%20there%2C%20is%20relying%20on%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20recently%20called%20on%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Tejashwi%2C%20to%20cement%20the%20bond.%20Given%20that%20the%20new%20Bihar%20in-charge%2C%20Allavaru%2C%20is%20not%20a%20heavyweight%20in%20the%20party%20and%20will%20likely%20work%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20AICC%20might%20mean%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20content%20to%20play%20second%20fiddle%20to%20regional%20parties%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20Puducherry%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoul-Searching%20Needed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%2015%20years%20back%2C%20V.%20Kishore%20Chandra%20Deo%2C%20who%20was%20General%20Secretary%20in%20charge%20of%20Bihar%2C%20had%20insisted%20that%20the%20party%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20doormat%E2%80%9D%20for%20Lalu's%20RJD%20in%20the%20state.%20Many%20would%20argue%20against%20that%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20herein%20lies%20the%20party's%20key%20affliction.%20There%20has%20not%20been%20a%20single%20soul-searching%20exercise%20in%20the%20Congress%20since%20May%202014%2C%20when%20the%20emergence%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20national%20scene%20resulted%20in%20the%20Congress's%20near-decimation.%20The%20formation%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20in%20itself%20yet%20another%20admission%20that%20the%20Congress%20cannot%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20on%20its%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20problems%20run%20deep%2C%20which%20mere%20cosmetic%20changes%20cannot%20fix.%20The%20appointment%20of%20two%20general%20secretaries%20and%20nine%20in-charges%20is%20hardly%20enough%20to%20enthuse%20workers.%20They%20may%20be%20trusted%20lieutenants%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20whether%20they%20will%20be%20useful%20to%20the%20organisation%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20future%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20looks%20uncertain%20and%20the%20party%20is%20staring%20at%20an%20existential%20crisis%20in%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20is%20debatable.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20party%20president%20Kharge%20has%20already%20warned%20the%20new%20appointees%20that%C2%A0office-bearers%20would%20be%20held%20%E2%80%9Caccountable%E2%80%9D%20for%20future%20elections%20in%20their%20respective%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20a%20team%20is%20as%20good%20as%20its%20leader.%20More%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20this%20experiment%20can%20be%20as%20much%20a%20test%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20for%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn