mitted%20to%20being%20drunk%20during%20the%20incident%20and%20claims%20to%20have%20fired%20multiple%20rounds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ADVITYA%20BAHL%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fnoida%2Fcity-resident-a-lawyer-held-for-boys-death-in-celebratory-firing%2Farticleshow%2F118393577.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Built%20by%205%20Friends%2C%20This%20Village%20School%20in%20Uttarakhand%20Uses%20Films%20%26amp%3B%20Debates%20To%20Make%20Learning%20Fun%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kamlesh%20Joshi%20joined%20Delhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20Dyal%20Singh%20College%20in%202007%20to%20pursue%20an%20honours%20degree%20in%20physics%2C%20he%20quickly%20realised%20two%20things.%20First%2C%20he%20had%20no%20real%20interest%20in%20the%20sciences%20and%20had%20chosen%20the%20subject%20primarily%20due%20to%20family%20pressure.%20Second%2C%20the%20gap%20between%20him%20and%20his%20peers%20at%20Delhi%20University%20was%20more%20like%20a%20valley%20than%20a%20schism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20his%20experience%20a%20culture%20shock%20would%20be%20an%20understatement%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20about%20this%20new%20environment%20was%20unfamiliar%20to%20him%2C%20coming%20from%20a%20rural%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20cope%2C%20and%20despite%20opposition%20from%20his%20family%2C%20he%20dropped%20out%20after%20his%20first%20year%20and%20switched%20to%20political%20science%20at%20Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh%20College.%20But%20this%20too%20proved%20challenging%3A%20transitioning%20to%20an%20entirely%20new%20field%20(having%20studied%20science%20in%20school)%2C%20and%20much%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341068%2Fteach-spoken-english-on-youtube-dehati-madam-uttar-pradesh-yashoda-lodhi-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20was%20conducted%20in%20English%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whereas%20he%20had%20attended%20a%20Hindi-medium%20school%20(Saraswati%20Vidya%20Mandir%2C%20Nanakmatta%2C%20Uttarakhand).%20Many%20lectures%20went%20over%20his%20head%20%E2%80%9Clike%20a%20bouncer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FTBI-featured-image-1_11zon-1739973158.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nanakmatta%20Public%20School%20was%20established%20to%20impart%20education%20that%20aligned%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20and%20the%20world.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FTBI-featured-image-1_11zon-1739973158.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FTBI-featured-image-1_11zon-1739973158-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FTBI-featured-image-1_11zon-1739973158-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FTBI-featured-image-1_11zon-1739973158-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FTBI-featured-image-1_11zon-1739973158-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-407347%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENanakmatta%20Public%20School%20was%20established%20to%20impart%20education%20that%20aligns%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20time%20to%20fill%20out%20examination%20forms%2C%20he%20kept%20them%20