1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22385%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EElephants%20migrated%20to%20the%20Udanti-Sitanadi%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20food%20and%20shelter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EM%3C%2Fem%3Eunaadi%20alert%20system%20was%20used%2C%20in%20which%20a%20%3Cem%3EKotwar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20village%20messenger)%20beat%20drums%20and%20used%20a%20microphone%20to%20warn%20villagers%20of%20approaching%20elephants.%20However%2C%20in%20April%202022%2C%20a%20tragic%20incident%20highlighted%20the%20limitations%20of%20this%20method.%20An%20elephant%20unexpectedly%20changed%20direction%2C%20entering%20a%20village%20that%20had%20not%20been%20warned%20in%20time%2C%20leading%20to%20three%20human%20casualties%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20my%20first%20time%20witnessing%20a%20human%20fatality%2C%20and%20I%20was%20there%20for%20the%20post-mortem%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20me.%20I%20realised%20we%20needed%20a%20faster%2C%20more%20reliable%20alert%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20AI%20into%20the%20picture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20find%20a%20technological%20solution%2C%20Varun%20and%20his%20team%20developed%20a%20basic%20application%20in%20February%202023.%20The%20system%20collected%20elephant%20movement%20data%20from%20foot%20patrolling%20teams%20and%20shared%20it%20with%20villagers%20via%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Varun%20soon%20connected%20with%20Kalpvaig%20Technologies%2C%20a%20Ghaziabad-based%20startup%2C%20which%20suggested%20automati