ing%20India%20to%20Thai%20flavours%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chef%20Garima%20isn%E2%80%99t%20being%20adventurous%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20she%20is%20kept%20on%20her%20toes%20by%20her%20son.%20Walking%20the%20tightrope%20between%20being%20a%20world-renowned%20chef%20and%20a%20full-time%20mom%20is%20a%20tricky%20balancing%20act.%20But%20she%20brings%20a%20finesse%20to%20it.%20When%20I%20credit%20her%20for%20this%2C%20she%20responds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20told%20that%20they%20can%20do%20everything.%20We%20already%20know%20we%20are%20capable.%20We%20have%20been%20doing%20it%20for%20years.%20It%20is%20the%20people%20around%20the%20woman%20who%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20support%20is%20integral.%20Most%20women%20stop%20pushing%20forward%20when%20that%20support%20system%20crumbles.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchef-garima-arora-4-1739878904.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20unique%20take%20on%20a%20classic%20Thai%20salad%20(L)%20and%20the%20lamb%20pad%20cha%20(R)%20are%20some%20of%20the%20signature%20dishes%20at%20Banng%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchef-garima-arora-4-1739878904.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchef-garima-arora-4-1739878904-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchef-garima-arora-4-1739878904-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchef-garima-arora-4-1739878904-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchef-garima-arora-4-1739878904-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406961%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628