2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehra%20took%20over%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20agricultural%20land%20and%20insisted%20on%20ploughing%20the%20fields%20himself.%20For%20years%2C%20he%20stuck%20to%20traditional%20farming%20methods%2C%20using%20pesticides%2C%20to%20maximise%20yield%20and%20profit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20a%20new%20wheat%20variety%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20Mehra%20noticed%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20agricultural%20habits%20around%20him.%20He%20saw%20more%20and%20more%20farmers%20were%20moving%20towards%20growing%20cash%20crops%20like%20soybeans%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F401509%2Fusing-tomato-waste-this-startup-creates-a-sustainable-replacement-for-animal-leather%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20up%20on%20wheat%20or%20grain%20crops.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%2C%20if%20we%20continue%20like%20this%2C%20if%20the%20country%20continues%20like%20this%2C%20what%20are%20we%20going%20to%20eat%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20he%20was%20cultivating%20the%20RR21%20wheat%20variety%2C%20which%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20good%20crop%E2%80%9D%3B%20but%20then%20something%20remarkable%20caught%20his%20eye.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20sowing%20his%20crops%2C%20he%20noticed%20some%20plants%20that%20looked%20different.%20That%20stalk%20of%20wheat%20looked